  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a non-stick pan over medium heat.",
    "Add garlic and cook until fragrant, about 1 minute.",
    "Gently fold orange segments into the pan with the garlic.",
    "Pour water and tamari sauce over the top of oranges and garlic, stirring well to combine.",
    "Add gluten-free bread crumbs and orange blossom water. Stir in salt and pepper.",
    "Simmer for 2-3 minutes until thickened slightly."
